n-convex objective functions and constraints. Extensive\nsimulation performance analysis has been carried out that validates the\nefficiency of the proposed solution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Aug 2017 06:39:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-16"}
