he role of dynein motors in the formation of the final concentric pattern. The\ninterplay between the passive and active mechanisms regulates the rate of the\naccumulation process, which in the absence of one them proceeds either too\nquickly or slowly.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Aug 2017 06:42:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-06"}
