gramming technique for graph isomorphism (STOC 1999) can be\nadapted to slightly improve the worst-case time complexity of the alternating\nmatrix space isometry problem in a certain range of parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Aug 2017 14:04:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 1 Oct 2017 12:48:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-03"}
